373
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:16,710
Actually,

374
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,310
I envy you.

375
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:20,800
Do you?

376
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:24,820
