503
00:23:44,230 --> 00:23:45,470
Go back and rest.

504
00:23:53,220 --> 00:23:56,860
[Sword Manor]

505
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,000
Leader! Leader!

506
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:57,800
What's the matter?

507
00:23:57,800 --> 00:23:58,950
Chong Xuezhi practiced Nine Moves of Lotus God

508
00:23:58,950 --> 00:24:01,040
