513
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:09,350
What?

514
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,160
Yes.

515
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:14,880
Nine Moves of Lotus God?

516
00:24:16,070 --> 00:24:18,190
