523
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,140
If the message is true,

524
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:36,490
Chong Xuezhi’s prestige will be improved

525
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:37,710
among the people.

526
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:40,310
The Hall of Flames

527
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:42,520
