528
00:24:43,710 --> 00:24:44,910
Let me see the leader!

529
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:46,430
Let me see the leader!

530
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,800
The witch Chong Xuezhi practiced Nine Moves of Lotus God

531
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,000
and killed my leader.

532
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:58,640
Mr. Lin, please uphold justice for my leader.

533
00:25:04,760 --> 00:25:05,890
Tell me the details.

534
00:25:06,310 --> 00:25:07,160
The other day,

535
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,830
