558
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:47,480
before I find out the killer.

559
00:25:48,950 --> 00:25:50,010
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

560
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:52,040
My leader died suspiciously.

561
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,760
