563
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:01,680
Qingmei.

564
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:03,490
Come with me.

565
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,280
Qingmei.

566
00:26:35,190 --> 00:26:36,680
You met Mr. Tie Xiao

567
00:26:37,590 --> 00:26:38,470
before he died.

568
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,450
